{"tid":2299394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國經濟五大命脈　全靠香港　任一項　都可使中國　爆體而亡","createTime":"2020-11-24T17:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T18:23:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"787b75577abce767bebe77a1b5bcba4d400added","tid":2299394,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158655862897357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158655862897357&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e3fbc6f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158655862897357</a><br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n理解經濟的人會做到，其他人要配合<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n大家有了概念，但金融對大多數人來說當然陌生<br />\n<br />\nSian Lo Lung:<br />\n<br />\n中國7成外資來自香港，現在中國企業被美國封殺，只能來港上市，更依賴香港金融市場。<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行借出了4萬億港元予中國。<br />\n<br />\n根據金管局網站資訊，香港是全球最龐大的離岸人民幣資金池，超過6500億元人民幣，全球70%以上人民幣通過香港結算。<br />\n<br />\n中國經濟學家在中國傳媒說，香港的人民幣進出是一個因素，影響人民幣匯率，而匯率影響中國國內通脹物價。"},{"pid":"ee54078c506901d0c9f37372b094c503e8979743","tid":2299394,"uid":282637,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"Fake News拉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iGXSmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iGXSmr.jpg&h=f95e008a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HBmxwFv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHBmxwFv.gif&h=7dda01cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6aa5a3804f8b6c0d6b5e8bff603e8c87d8992795","tid":2299394,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"但上至中共,下至少數派,都想香港死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d775da760c7851ff72db9a802cbe024b579a621","tid":2299394,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6aa5a3804f8b6c0d6b5e8bff603e8c87d8992795","